{"tid":607841,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都試過叫野食，但份量係完全接受唔到，但又要硬食","createTime":"2018-03-27T15:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T16:35:04.000Z","uid":150822,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f66d5ce82be6357fefc5e6eaf3b439e2d61dd671","tid":607841,"uid":150822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/27/231337_58fe3431526d6ac43240d0327bd53f26.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F27%2F231337_58fe3431526d6ac43240d0327bd53f26.png&h=6b1a9212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，幾日前係元氣叫左呢個雞軟骨 $26 拎到黎就係咁既樣 少都算 十足十比人食過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗無人會認同呢碟野既份量係值呢個價錢呱？<br />\n但本住寧得罪拉登 莫得罪整野食比你既人<br />\n加上我只係一條無膽毒L<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n靜靜咁食埋佢就算....但以後真係唔會再叫呢碟野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！！！"},{"pid":"5ac9e99c89d25e128ae1c04096f6c51e57a8d9fd","tid":607841,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T15:23:43.000Z","msg":"牛肉薯餅又平又正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ead07a4e1ceec6b75814da473d7ea939ca1d1b","tid":607841,"uid":155306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:33:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/28/003328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F28%2F003328_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=d8911074&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9bb893b84947e6e78d6283549506e1bb640e41","tid":607841,"uid":174074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:34:17.000Z","msg":"元氣啲湯鳥冬先最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmo